      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, making it a reliable and comfortable choice for its next owner. The engine runs smoothly, the transmission shifts seamlessly, and all major mechanical systems are in solid working order. The exterior shows only minor signs of regular use, while the interior remains clean and well-preserved. It is a dependable daily driver that has many miles of service left to offer.",
