    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair, functional condition and is an ideal choice for a buyer looking for a reliable daily driver where utility is more important than a perfect appearance. The exterior has several visible surface scratches and a few small dings consistent with its age and regular use. Inside, the cabin shows noticeable wear on the upholstery and some trim pieces, but all essential features and controls remain fully operational. It has been maintained to ensure it runs dependably, making it a solid, honest car for someone who needs practical transportation.",
      "price": 23500.0,
