      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in true showroom condition. This car has been pampered in a climate-controlled environment and looks exactly as it did the day it was delivered. The exterior finish is flawless, with deep, glass-like paint clarity and absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings. The wheels are pristine with zero curb rash, wrapped in high-performance tires with ample tread. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and matte, free from any creases or wear patterns. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the ambient lighting, operates with factory precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by certified technicians. This car drives tight, quiet, and powerful, offering the tactile feedback of a brand-new machine. It comes complete with a full service history, two sets of keys, and all original owner\u2019s manuals. For the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the one.",
      "price": 46800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
